SYNOPSIS
        varargs string break_string(string sWhat, int iLength,
          int iIndent, status tNoFirst)

DESCRIPTION
        Breaks a continous string without newlines into a string
        with newlines inserted at regular intervals replacing spaces.
        Each newline separeted string can be indented with a given
        number of spaces.
        sWhat: Original message
        iLength: The total maximum width of each line
        iIndent: (optional) How many spaces to indent with
        tNoFirst: (optional) Don't indent the first line
        Returns: A string with newline separated strings
